    participant User as ğŸ‘¤ User<br/>(Browser)
    participant Frontend as ğŸŒ Frontend<br/>React App
    participant Gateway as âš¡ API Gateway<br/>Port 8000
    participant UserSvc as ğŸ‘¤ User Service<br/>Port 8001
    participant JobProc as âš™ï¸ Job Processor<br/>Port 8003
    participant SvcReg as ğŸ“‹ Service Registry<br/>Port 8002
    participant DB as ğŸ—„ï¸ PostgreSQL
